{
  "text": "DUX4s transcripts are produced in both control and FSHD muscle. DUX4fl mRNA and DUX4 protein expression is not seen in most somatic tissues but is consistently observed in a lowproportion (∼1 out of every 1000) FSHD muscle cells [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Although DUX4fl transcripts have also been reported in control muscle, these are much less frequently observed and are present at much lower levels [CITATION_3] , suggesting that there is a threshold above which DUX4fl levels cause FSHD.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "29814597",
